The [[phoneme]] inventory of the '''[[Marathi language]]''' is similar to that of many other [[Indo-Aryan languages]]. An [[International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]] chart of all contrastive sounds in Marathi is provided below.

== Vowels ==
Vowels in native words are:

