== Consonant clusters ==
In Marathi, the consonants by default come with a [[schwa]]. Therefore, तयाचे will be <nowiki>'təyāce'</nowiki>, not <nowiki>'tyāce'</nowiki>. To form <nowiki>'tyāce'</nowiki>, one should add त् to याचे, which would yield त्याचे.

